Uses of Package
com.nerjal.json

  • Packages that use com.nerjal.json 
    Package Description
    com.nerjal.json
    This package provides the ability to instantiate and manipulate JSON structures within Java.
    com.nerjal.json.elements
    This package provides all the tools to build and manipulate JSON structures within Java.
    com.nerjal.json.mapper  
    com.nerjal.json.parser
    This package provides all the required tools to properly parse any string or file to JSON and vice-versa.
    com.nerjal.json.parser.options
    This package holds all the stringification options classes for all the com.nerjal.json.elements' element classes.
  • Classes in com.nerjal.json used by com.nerjal.json 
    Class and Description
    JsonError.JsonElementTypeException
    Thrown when trying to get a typed element from a JsonElement which isn't of the corresponding type.
    JsonError.JsonParseException
    Thrown when trying to parse an invalid String to a JsonElement
    JsonError.RecursiveJsonElementException
    Thrown when trying to stringify a JsonElement containing itself.
  • Classes in com.nerjal.json used by com.nerjal.json.elements 
    Class and Description
